												<div class="article-snippet_thematique">Economie</div>							<div class="article-snippet_date">01 Avril<span class="article-snippet_hour"> Ã  17h45</span></div>				<h3 class="article-snippet_title article-snippet_title--m"><a href="/edition/wsj/japon-s-endette-en-toute-zenitude-182747" class="article-snippet_link">Le Japon sâendette en toute zÃ©nitude</a></h3>							<div class="article-snippet_author">Megumi Fujikawa et Kosaku Narioka</div>			</div>
</div>
        </li>
          </ul>
